        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>currentMode</name>
        <initializer>= STANDBY</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Global variable to track the current mode of the EEPROM (READ, WRITE, or STANDBY) </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This variable is used to keep track of the current mode of the EEPROM so that the setMode function can avoid unnecessary pin reconfigurations if the EEPROM is already in the desired mode. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
